%N A016055 Inverse of 2046th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A016055 Periodic with period length 2046. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A016055 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A016055/b016055.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..3000</a>
%H A016055 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 2046.
%H A016055 <a href="/index/Rec#order_600">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, order 600.
%H A016055 <a href="/index/Pol#poly_cyclo_inv">Index to sequences related to inverse of cyclotomic polynomials</a>
%p A016055 with(numtheory,cyclotomic); c := n->series(1/cyclotomic(n,x),x,80);
